How does Busuu work?

   Learn the smart way

   Over 1000 lessons created by expert linguists enhanced with machine
   learning technology like personalized study plans and speech
   recognition.
   Learn the smart way
   Get feedback from native speakers

   Connect with over 90 million learners and native speakers. Get instant
   feedback on written and spoken lessons from our global community.
   Get feedback from native speakers

